{
  "newspaper_id": "ada-lk",
  "url": "https://www.ada.lk/technology/\u0da9\u0dba\u0dbd\u0ddc\u0d9c\u0dca-\u0d91\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7\u0db4\u200d\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca--VDOmeet-\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0da9\u0dd2\u0dba\u0ddd-\u0d8b\u0db4\u0daf\u0dda\u0dc1\u0db1-\u0dc3\u0dda\u0dc0\u0dcf-\u0dc3\u0db3\u0dc4\u0dcf-\u0db4\u0dc4\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0d9a\u0db8\u0dca-\u0dc3\u0dbd\u0dc3\u0dba\u0dd2/5-374210",
  "time_ut": 1611325981,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0da9\u0dba\u0dbd\u0ddc\u0d9c\u0dca \u0d91\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7\u0db4\u200d\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca  VDOmeet \u0dc0\u0dd3\u0da9\u0dd2\u0dba\u0ddd \u0d8b\u0db4\u0daf\u0dda\u0dc1\u0db1 \u0dc3\u0dda\u0dc0\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0db3\u0dc4\u0dcf \u0db4\u0dc4\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0d9a\u0db8\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dbd\u0dc3\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Dialog Enterprise facilitates VDOmeet video consulting services",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Continuing its contribution to the national efforts to combat Covid-19, Dialog Enterprises, the enterprise solutions company owned by Dialog Asiata plc, has empowered its business customers with VDOmeet video calling facility to serve their customers.",
        "Through the VDOmeet video call facility, a corporate or consulting service agency can initiate a video call to one of their clients through a link, and through this, the customer can click on the link and meet the person providing the service in a virtual way without meeting them in person.",
        "Adaptable to any operating system, this facility does not require any prior installation or download. In addition, this communication service facility is available through any mobile web browser, and corporate customers can record calls, take screen shots or watch recorded videos for up to 30 days from the date of calls and download those videos to their personal cloud storage on demand. It also has the additional facility of Customers can sign up for VDOmeet by visiting http://vdomeet.lk/.",
        "The covid 19 global epidemic has caused a rapid change in the country's communication practices. In addition to serving professionals and institutions, the VDOmeet facility also facilitates a flexible system for the education sector through which teachers and academic staff can confirm that their students' studies are going on without interruption, as well as providing a viable and sustainable solution for the health sector and its healthcare professionals. As another unique facility introduced by Dialog to empower the national mission to combat the global pandemic of Covid-19.",
        "Not only that, the VDOmeet facility has also been able to add value to telecommunications companies in Sri Lanka that are moving towards digital transformation. For more information visit http://vdomeet.lk/, http://vdomeet.lk/"
      ],
